<Layout title="Adam McKenna Portfolio">
  <header>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Adam McKenna</h1>
    <h2 class="font-semibold mt-2 text-xl">Web Developer</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-base">
      I'm a remote full-stack developer with a passion for <strong
        >user experience</strong
      >, <strong>accessibility</strong> and <strong>service design</strong>.
    </p>

    <nav class="max-md:hidden">
      <ul>
        <li><a class="block" href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a class="block mt-2" href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
        <li><a class="block mt-2" href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
        <li><a class="block mt-2" href="#career-breaks">Career Breaks</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <ul class="mt-4 flex gap-2 opacity-75">
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/adam-mckenna" target="_blank"
          ><img class="w-7" src="./icons/github.svg" /></a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://dev.to/adammckenna" target="_blank"
          ><img class="w-7" src="./icons/dev-to.svg" /></a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-mckenna/" target="_blank"
          ><img class="w-7" src="./icons/linkedin.svg" /></a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://adam-mckenna.medium.com/" target="_blank"
          ><img class="w-7" src="./icons/medium.svg" /></a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/adamcantrun" target="_blank"
          ><img class="w-7" src="./icons/insta.svg" /></a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </header>

  <section>
    <section class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-semibold" id="about">About</h2>

      <p class="mt-2 text-base">
        Like many developers, my coding life <strong
          >began about 10 years ago</strong
        > building basic PHP websites with WordPress. Then I discovered how <strong
          >great JavaScript is</strong
        >. Since then, I've been lucky enough to write JavaScript for a <strong
          ><a href="https://www.merkle.com/dach/en">large Germany agency</a
          ></strong
        >, a <strong
          ><a href="https://www.binaryvision.com/">small English agency</a
          ></strong
        >, the <strong
          ><a href="https://dwpdigital.blog.gov.uk/">UK government</a></strong
        > and a <strong
          ><a href="https://moneyadvicetrust.org/">debt-support charity</a
          ></strong
        >.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-3 text-base">
        These days, after a <a href="#career-breaks"
          >sabbatical to travel the world</a
        >, I'm working mostly with frontend stuff with a real focus on creating <strong
          >highly usable and accessible applications</strong
        > with a focus on <strong>slick service design</strong>. <strong
          ><a href="https://react.dev/">React</a></strong
        > is my forte. But I work with other technologies, including backend stuff,
        as needed.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-3 text-base">
        Outside of work, I'm a <strong
          ><a href="https://www.instagram.com/adamcantrun">keen runner</a
          ></strong
        >, the <strong>household chef</strong> and a bit of a <strong
          >coffee snob</strong
        >. I've always got a <strong
          ><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/62146817-adam-mckenna"
            >few books on the go</a
          ></strong
        >, too.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-semibold" id="experience">Experience</h2>

      <!-- ToDo: implement timeline at the side -->
      <article class="mt-4">
        <p class="text-xs opacity-75 flex">
          AUG 2022 — MAR 2023 <span class="mx-1 text-[7px] opacity-75"
            >&#x2022;</span
          > London, England
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mt-1 flex flex-wrap">
          Web Developer <span class="mx-2 text-[11px] opacity-75">&#x2022;</span
          >
          <a
            class="text-black no-underline inline-flex"
            href="https://binaryvision.com/"
            target="_blank"
            >Binary Vision <img
              class="inline-block ml-1 w-2"
              src="./icons/external-link.svg"
              alt=""
            /></a
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm/6">
          Developed and maintained a <strong>data visualisation PWA</strong> for
          <a href="https://www.oxinst.com/" target="_blank">
            Oxford Instruments</a
          >. Worked closely with the <strong>client</strong>, <strong
            >designers</strong
          > and the
          <strong>development team</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap mt-3 gap-1.5 opacity-75">
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            React
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            Next.js
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            HTML
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            CSS
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            PWA
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-xs opacity-75 flex">
          APR 2021 — APR 2022 <span class="mx-1 text-[7px] opacity-75"
            >&#x2022;</span
          > Sheffield, England
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mt-1 flex flex-wrap">
          Senior Frontend Developer <span class="mx-2 text-[11px] opacity-75"
            >&#x2022;</span
          >
          <a
            class="text-black no-underline inline-flex"
            href="https://dwpdigital.blog.gov.uk/"
            target="_blank"
            >DWP Digital <img
              class="inline-block ml-1 w-2"
              src="./icons/external-link.svg"
              alt=""
            /></a
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm/6">
          Worked across several teams on <strong>internal tools</strong> for authentication
          and customer management. Worked with the <a
            href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/"
            target="_blank">GOV.UK Design System</a
          >.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap mt-3 gap-1.5 opacity-75">
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            React
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            HTML
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            CSS
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            Jest
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            Node.js
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-xs opacity-75 flex">
          JAN 2020 — APR 2021 <span class="mx-1 text-[7px] opacity-75"
            >&#x2022;</span
          > Birmingham, England
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mt-1 flex flex-wrap">
          Frontend Developer <span class="mx-2 text-[11px] opacity-75"
            >&#x2022;</span
          >
          <a
            class="text-black no-underline inline-flex"
            href="https://moneyadvicetrust.org/"
            target="_blank"
            >Money Advice Trust <img
              class="inline-block ml-1 w-2"
              src="./icons/external-link.svg"
              alt=""
            /></a
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm/6">
          De-facto frontend lead for a series of <a
            href="https://www.cloudflare.com/en-gb/learning/performance/static-site-generator/"
            >static-site generated</a
          > builds for a <strong>debt-support charity</strong>. Worked with <strong
            >Next.js</strong
          >, <strong>Gatsby</strong> and a supporting <strong
            >Python backend</strong
          >.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap mt-3 gap-1.5 opacity-75">
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            React
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            Next.js
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            Gatsby
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            HTML
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            CSS
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            Python
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <a
        href="./adam-mckenna-cv.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex font-semibold no-underline mt-6"
        >View complete resume <img
          class="inline-block ml-2 w-4"
          src="./icons/external-link-horizontal.svg"
          alt=""
        /></a
