        <img
          alt="Oxford Instruments Viewpoint UI sample"
          class="mt-4 rounded"
          src="./viewpoint.png"
        />
      </article>

      <article class="mt-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold flex flex-wrap">
          <a
            class="text-black no-underline inline-flex"
            href="https://www.merkle.com/dach/en/references/siemens-analytics-unlocked"
            target="_blank"
            >Siemens Analytics Unlocked <img
              class="inline-block ml-1 w-2"
              src="./icons/external-link.svg"
              alt=""
            /></a
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm/6">
          Analytics Unlocked is an <strong
            >award-winning data visualisation</strong
          > platform to simplify complex marketing data from <strong
            >Siemens</strong
          > across the globe.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap mt-3 gap-1.5 opacity-75">
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            React
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
          >
            HTML
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded bg-support text-support-light py-0.5 px-2 text-xs transition-all"
