          <strong>20-month sabbatical</strong> to work, volunteer and travel across
          <strong>14 countries</strong> and <strong>3 continents</strong>.
          Cheffed for 6 months and volunteered across 8 projects.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="mt-6">
        <p class="text-xs opacity-75 flex">
          APR 2022 — JUL 2022 <span class="mx-1 text-[7px] opacity-75"
