        </p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mt-1 flex flex-wrap">
          Chef <span class="mx-2 text-[11px] opacity-75">&#x2022;</span>
          <a
            class="text-black no-underline inline-flex"
            href="https://gustorestaurants.com/"
            target="_blank"
            >Gusto Italians <img
              class="inline-block ml-1 w-2"
              src="./icons/external-link.svg"
              alt=""
            /></a
          >
        </h3>

        <p class="mt-1 text-sm/6">
          <strong>3-month sabbatical</strong> from work to explore my passion for
          cooking. Responsible for preparing, cooking and plating starters, salads
          and desserts. We did as many as <strong>300 covers a day</strong>.
