        </p>

        <img
          src="/headshot.jpg"
          class="mt-4"
          style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;width: 160px; height: 160px; border-radius: 100px; background: grey"
        />
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12">
        <p class="text-sm/6 font-extralight text-primary-dark-opaque">
          Designed and developed by myself. Designed with <a
            href="https://www.figma.com/">Figma</a
          >. Developed with <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a>, <a
            href="https://react.dev/">React</a
          > and <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwind</a>. Deployed with <a
            href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel</a
